1 spros bral don gsal chen po'i rgyud spros bral don gsal chen po'i rgyud ces bya ba
2 rgyud thams cad kyi rtse rgyal nam mkha' 'bar ba'i rgyud rgyud thams cad kyi rtse rgyal 'bar ba'i rgyud rgyud thams cad kyi rtse rgyal namkha' 'bar ba'i rgyud
3 rgyud thams cad kyi spyi phud nyi zla bkod pa nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud rgyud thams cad kyi spyi phud nyi zla bkod pa nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud rgyud thams cad kyi spyi phud nyi zla bkod pa dang mnyam pa'i rgyud
4 nam mkha' 'brug sgrog thog babs klong 'dus spyi rgyal rgya mdud kyi rgyud nam mkha' 'brug sgrog thog babs klong 'dus spyi rgyal rgya mdud rgyud brug sgrogs thog babs klog 'dus spyi rgyal rgya mdud rgyud namkha' 'brug sgrog thog babs glog 'dus spyi rgyal 'phrul gyi rgya mdud kyi rgyud
5 lta ba la shan chen po rin chen sgron ma rtsa ba'i rgyud
6 rtsa rlung thig le'i rgyud rtsa lung rgyud 'jam dpal 'dus pa'i rgyud las bsdus pa
7 sangs rgyas thig le nyag gcig
8 srog gi 'khor lo'i rgyud pa yang ti nag po srog gi 'khor lo'i rgyud le med
9 yang gsang lta ba la thal gyi rgyud/ kun tu bzang po'i srog gi spu gri/ rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs kyi reg chod/ ro langs bde ba'i thugs kyi srog gi thigs pa/ brgyud pa gsum pa lta ba la thal gyi rgyud lta ba la thal gyi rgyud
10 spyod pa thabs dang shes rab kyi rgyud/ srog gi thigs pa bdud rtsi'i bum pa/ snang byed kyi spu gri'i rgyud/ yang ti nag po'i rgyud/ rim pa nas snyan du brgyud pa/ spyod pa'i rgyud/ thig le'i ngang las shar ba yi/ thabs dang shes rab kyi rgyud/ srog gi thigs pa/_bdud rtsi'i bum pa/ snang byed kyi spu gri'i rgyud yang ti gser gyi 'bru gcig pa snang byed spu gri'i rgyud
11 kun bzang srog gi thigs pa 'bras bu ye grol chen po'i rgyud kun bzang srog gi thig pa 'bras bu ye grol chen po'i rgyud
12 thig le mthong brtol gyi rgyud thig le mthong brtol gyi rgyud/ rig pa bcur 'byung gi brda'/ srog gi 'chan pa/ yang ti nag po'i rgyud thig le mthong brtol gyi rgyud/ rig pa bcur 'byung gi brda'/ srog gi chan pa/ yang ti nag po'i rgyud yang ti nag po thig le mthong brtol gyi rgyud rig pa bcud byung gi brda' srog gi chan pa
13 rgyud kyi rtse rgyal nyi zla 'od 'bar mkha' klong rnam dag rgya mtsho klong gsal rgyud rgyud kyi rgyal po nyi zla 'od 'bar mkha' klong rnam dag rgya mtsho klong gsal gyi rgyud zhes bya ba
14 rdo rje sems dpa' yi ge brgya pa dbang mchog rgyal po'i rgyud ces bya ba rdo rje sems dpa'i yi ge brgya pa dbang mchog rgyal po'i rgyud
15 rdo rje sems dpa' yi ge brgya pa thugs phrin las thams cad kyi dam tshig gi rgyud ces bya rdo rje sems dpa' yi ge brgya pa thugs phrin las thams cad kyi dam tshig gi rgyud rdo rje sems dpa'/yi ge brgya pa'i rgyud/ thugs 'phrin las tham.d dam tshig gi rgyud ces bya ba
16 rdzogs pa chen po nges don 'dus pa'i rgyud/ lta ba thams cad kyi snying po rin po che rnam par bkod pa rdzogs pa chen po nges don 'dus pa'i rgyud/ lta ba thams cad kyi snying po rin po che rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba
17 rdzogs pa chen po rin po che 'khor ba rtsad gcod kyi rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs pa chen po rin po che 'khor ba rtsad gcod kyi rgyud rdzogs pa chen po 'khor ba btsad gcod kyi rgyud
18 rdzogs pa chen po 'khor ba rtsad nas gcod pa chos sku skye med rig pa'i rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs pa chen po 'khor ba rtsad nas gcod pa chos sku skye med rig pa'i rgyud
19 rdzogs pa chen po lta ba'i yang snying / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa / nam mkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs pa chen po lta ba'i yang snying / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa/ klong yangs kyi rgyud rdzogs pa chen po lta ba'i yang snying// sangyas tham.d kyi dgongs pa// namkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud ces bya ba
20 rdzogs pa chen po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa chos sku gcig tu 'dus par bka' bgros pa'i don / rin po che yon tan kun 'byung gi rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs pa chen po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa chos sku gcig tu 'dus par bka' bgros pa'i don rin po che yon tan kun 'byung gi rgyud rdzogs pa chen po sangyas tham.d kyi dgongs pa chos sku gcig tu 'dus par bka' bgros pa'i don// rin po che yton kun 'byung gi rgyud ces bya ba
21 rdzogs pa chen po shin tu rnal 'byor sangs rgyas thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyud / ye shes chos kyi sku don 'dus rig pa'i gsung */ gsang ba thugs kyi ting nge 'dzin / rang byung bde ba 'khor lo mthar phyin 'bras bu'i rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs pa chen po shin tu rnal 'byor sangs rgyas thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyud/ ye shes chos kyi sku/ don 'dus rig pa'i gsung/ gsang ba thugs kyi ting 'dzin/ rang 'byung bde ba'i 'khor lo/ mthar phyin 'bras bu'i rgyud/ rdzogs pa chen po shin tu rnal 'byor sangs rgyas thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyud// ye shes chos kyi sku// don 'dus rigs pa'i gsung// gsang ba thugs kyi ting 'dzin ni// rang 'byung bde ba'i 'khor lo// mthar phyin 'bras bu'i / rgyud ces bya ba
22 rdzogs pa chen po nges don 'dus pa'i yang snying */ kun tu bzang po ye shes klong gi rgyud / rin po che gser gyi yang zhun zhes bya ba rdzogs pa chen po nges don 'dus pa'i yang snying/ kun tu bzang po ye shes klong gi rgyud/ rin po che gser gyi yang zhun rdzogs pa chen po nges don 'dus pa'i yang snying / kun tu bzang po /ye shes klong gi rgyud/ rin po che gser gyi yang zhun zhes bya ba
23 rdzogs pa chen po nges don thams cad 'dus pa / ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud / lta bsgom thams cad kyi snying po / rin po che rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba rdzogs pa chen po nges don thams cad 'dus pa/ ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud/ lta sgom thams cad kyi snying po rin po che rnam par bkod pa rdzogs pa chen po nges don thams cad 'dus pa/ ye shes namkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud/ lta sgom thams cad kyi snying po/ /mnyam pa nyid kyi rgyal po
24 rdzogs pa chen po don 'dus rig pa'i gsung rang byung bde ba'i 'khor lo zhes bya ba rdzogs pa chen po don 'dus rig pa'i gsung rang byung bde ba'i 'khor lo rdzogs pa chen po don 'dus pa'i rig pa'i gsung rang byung bde ba'i 'khor lo zhes bya ba
25 rdzogs pa chen po ma rig mun pa rab tu sel bar byed pa'i lta ba ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud ces bya ba rdzogs pa chen po ma rig mun pa rab tu sel bar byed pa'i lta ba ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud rdzogs pa chen po ma rig mun pa rab tu sel bar byed pa'i lta ba // ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud ces bya ba

44 thugs kyi yang snying dgongs pa'i bcud 'dus pa / bka' rgyud rnams kyi gsang don bcud dril ba ma rig mun sel nyi zla 'bar ba'i rgyud thugs kyi yang snying dgongs pa'i bcud 'dus pa/ ka dag rnams kyi gsang don bcud dril ba/ ma rig mun sel nyi zla 'bar ba'i rgyud thugs kyi yang snying dgongs pa'i bcud 'dus pa/ ka dag rnams kyi gsang don bcud dril pa/ ma rig mun sel nyi zla 'bar ba'i rgyud thugs kyi dgongs pa'i bcud 'dus pa// ka dag rnams kyi gsang don bcudu dril pa/ ma rig mun sel nyi zla 'bar ba'i rgyud

47 rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po nyi zla'i snying po 'od 'bar ba bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho 'khyil pa'i rgyud rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po nyi zla'i snying po 'od 'bar ba bdud rtsi rgya mtsho 'khyil ba'i rgyud rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po nyi zla'i snying po 'od 'bar ba bdud rtsi rgya mtshor 'khyil ba'i rgyud

50 yi ge med pa'i rgyud chen po zhes bya ba / rin po che rgyal mtshan gyi rgyud / rgyal po'i gdung rgyud / lta ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud chen po yi ge med pa'i rgyud chen po zhes bya ba/ rin po che rgyal mtshan gyi rgyud/ rgyal po'i gdung rgyud/ lta ba nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud
51 de bzhin gshegs pa thams kyi ting nge 'dzin yongs su bshad pa / ye shes 'dus pa'i mdo / theg pa chen po / gsang ba bla na med pa'i rgyud / chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa / gsang sngags gcig pa'i ye shes / rdzogs pa chen po'i don gsal bar byed pa'i rgyud / rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud ces bya ba rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ting nge 'dzin dngos su bshad pa/ ye shes 'dus pa'i mdo/ theg pa chen po gsang ba bla na med pa'i rgyud/ chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas/ sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa/ gsang sngags sa cig pa'i ye shes/ rdzogs pa chen po don gsal bar byed pa'i rgyud/ rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud/
52 rig pa rang grol chen po thams cad 'grol ba'i rgyud ces bya ba rigs pa rang grol chen po/ thams cad grol ba'i rgyud
